---
import '../styles/site.css';
---

<html lang="es">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/images/logos/logo-transparent.png" />
		<title>Registro | Eco Negocios e Inversiones</title>
	</head>
	<body class="min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center relative p-4" style="background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(232,250,235,0.88) 0%, rgba(245,252,247,0.96) 100%), url('/images/greenprojects.png') center center/cover no-repeat;" data-page="register" data-auth-mode="register">
		<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-green-950/10 via-transparent to-emerald-500/10 pointer-events-none"></div>
		<div class="relative w-full max-w-md">
			<section class="bg-white/70 backdrop-blur-xl rounded-3xl p-6 md:p-8 shadow-2xl border border-white/30">
				<div class="flex items-center gap-3 md:gap-4 mb-5 md:mb-6">
					<img src="/images/logos/logo-transparent.png" alt="Eco Negocios" class="w-20 md:w-24 h-8 md:h-10 object-contain" />
					<div>
						<p class="text-xs text-green-600 uppercase tracking-widest font-bold">Firebase Auth</p>
						<h1 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-green-950" id="loginTitle">Crear cuenta</h1>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="rounded-2xl bg-emerald-50 border border-emerald-100 px-4 py-3 text-sm text-emerald-900 mb-5" id="loginHelper">
					Registrate con tu nombre y correo. Te enviaremos un vinculo seguro y al abrirlo se creara tu perfil como beneficiario.
				</div>

				<ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-green-800 mb-5" id="loginSteps">
					<li class="rounded-2xl bg-emerald-50 border border-emerald-100 px-4 py-3">1. Completa tu nombre y correo.</li>
					<li class="rounded-2xl bg-emerald-50 border border-emerald-100 px-4 py-3">2. Recibes un vinculo de acceso sin contrasena.</li>
					<li class="rounded-2xl bg-emerald-50 border border-emerald-100 px-4 py-3">3. Al abrirlo, activas tu cuenta y entras al dashboard.</li>
				</ul>

				<form id="loginForm" class="space-y-4">
					<label class="block" id="nameField">
						<span class="block text-sm font-bold text-green-900 mb-1">Nombre completo</span>
						<input type="text" name="name" placeholder="Tu nombre" class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-2xl border border-green-200 bg-white/90 text-base" required />
					</label>
					<label class="block">
						<span class="block text-sm font-bold text-green-900 mb-1">Correo</span>
						<input type="email" name="email" placeholder="usuario@eco.com" class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-2xl border border-green-200 bg-white/90 text-base" required />
					</label>
					<button type="submit" class="w-full py-3 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-green-600 to-emerald-400 text-white font-bold shadow-lg">Registrarme con mi correo</button>
					<p class="text-center text-sm min-h-5 font-medium" id="loginMessage"></p>
				</form>

				<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between mt-5 text-sm gap-2 text-green-700">
					<a href="/login" class="hover:text-green-900">Ya tengo cuenta</a>
					<a href="/" class="hover:text-green-900">Volver a la landing</a>
				</div>
			</section>
		</div>

		<script>
			import { initLoginPage } from '../scripts/login';

			initLoginPage();
		</script>
	</body>
</html>
